## Project

- Stack: React 18 + TypeScript + Vite, raw CSS with CSS variables, Zustand, TanStack Query, Motion, Swiper
- Code: `main/src/` | Accent: `#6C47FF` | Currency: ₦ only | Mobile-first CSS
- All inputs: `font-size: 16px` min. Never override below 16px.

---

## Hard-banned (auto-fail)

- Soft gradients as decoration
- Glassmorphism as default UI
- Corners > 10px cards / > 8px buttons / > 6px inputs
- Pill buttons everywhere
- 3-column equal feature cards
- `Inter` as default font — use `Geist`, `Outfit`, `Cabinet Grotesk`, `Satoshi`
- Em-dashes (`—`) anywhere
- Pure `#000` or `#fff`
- `window.addEventListener('scroll', ...)` — use `motion/react` `useScroll()`
- `useState` for scroll/mouse values — use `useMotionValue`
- Animating `top/left/width/height` — only `transform` and `opacity`
- Fake product UIs from `<div>` rectangles
- Hero sections inside dashboards
- Metric-card grid as dashboard default

---

## Writing

Default to "is." No trailing "-ing" clauses. No AI sign-offs.
Banned: additionally, crucial, delve, enhance, seamless, leverage, utilize, empower, revolutionize, groundbreaking, robust, showcase, pivotal, meticulous, journey (metaphorical), vibrant, nestled.
Full rules: `ai-rules/writing.md`

